data.description: WOW!!! HOME ON OVER AN ACRE SO BRING ALL YOUR TOYS AND YOUR LARGE FAMILY TOO BECAUSE IT ALSO HAS 4 BEDROOMS AND 3 BATHS!!! BUT WAIT!!! THAT'S NOT ALL!!! There is a 18x30 metal workshop/storage shed, RV covered storage area PLUS RV hook up or could also be great for a boat!! Fully fenced in backyard that would be perfect for a pool, play ground, Or for large BBQ parties with friends and family! Inside you will find vinyl plank flooring, corian countertops, split floor plan, and an area for a home office!!!
